summary: Entrepreneur, data scientist, and traveler. From a chaotic complex systems researcher, I turned into a business entrepreneur, founding and developing a success ski and wine tourism company, developing strong leadership and management skills in the last 12 years. I traveled to 500 destinations in 90 countries, living in Chile, Brazil, France, Spain, Russia and Japan, getting a multiple cultural understandings for international business.
